import React from 'react';
import ContractForm from "../ContractForm";
import { drizzleConnect } from "drizzle-react";
import { Form, Col, Button, Card, InputGroup, FormControl } from "react-bootstrap";
 
class NewResident extends React.Component {
	render() {
		return(
			<Card>
				<Form>
					<Form.Group controlId="name">
						<Form.Label>Nombre</Form.Label>
					    <Form.Control placeholder="Introduce tu nombre" />
					</Form.Group>

					<Form.Group controlId="email">
						<Form.Label>Email</Form.Label>
					    <Form.Control placeholder="Introduce tu email" />
					</Form.Group>

	  				<Form.Row>
					    <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="phone">
					      <Form.Label>Nombre</Form.Label>
					      <Form.Control placeholder="Introduce tu teléfono" />
					    </Form.Group>

					    <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="code">
					      <Form.Label>Código de Madrid Central</Form.Label>
					      <Form.Control placeholder="Introduce tu código de Madrid Central" />
					    </Form.Group>
	  				</Form.Row>

	  				<Form.Row>
					    <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="price">
					      <Form.Label>Precio</Form.Label>
					      <Form.Control placeholder="Elige un precio" />
					    </Form.Group>

					    <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="invitations">
					      <Form.Label>Número de invitaciones</Form.Label>
					      <Form.Control placeholder="Elige el número de invitaciones disponibles" />
					    </Form.Group>
	  				</Form.Row>
					<Button variant="primary" type="submit">
						Submit
					</Button>
				</Form>
				<InputGroup className="mb-3">
    				<InputGroup.Prepend>
      					<InputGroup.Text id="basic-addon1">@</InputGroup.Text>
    				</InputGroup.Prepend>
    				<FormControl
      					placeholder="Username"
      					aria-label="Username"
      					aria-describedby="basic-addon1"
    				/>
  				</InputGroup>
			</Card>
		);
	}
}

const mapStateToProps = state => {
  return {
    MadridCentral: state.contracts.MadridCentral,
    accounts: state.accounts
  };
};

export default drizzleConnect(NewResident, mapStateToProps);
